Start time:17:11:23 2009-03-13
Project: mobicents-jainslee-server-core
This class represents ProfileContext. Note that profile context object MUST belong to one profile table during its life time, profile(object) can change.
The ProfileContext interface provides a Profile object with access to SLEE-managed state that is dependent on the Profile objects's currently executing context. A ProfileContext object is given to a Profile object after the Profile object is created via the setProfileContext method. The ProfileContext object remains associated with the Profile object for the lifetime of that Profile object. Note that the information that the Profile object obtains from the ProfileContext object may change as the SLEE assigns the Profile object to different profiles during the Profile object's lifecycle.

Author:
Bartosz Baranowski , Alexandre Mendonca
